<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= @author.name %> - Biblioteca MÃ­stica</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
      :root {
          --primary-dark: #1a1a2e;
          --primary-blue: #16213e;
          --accent: #0f3460;
          --light-bg: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);
          --glass-bg: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);
          --border-light: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
          --text-primary: #1a202c;
          --text-secondary: #4a5568;
          --text-muted: #a0aec0;
      }

      * {
          box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
          background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-dark) 0%, var(--primary-blue) 50%, var(--accent) 100%);
          font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
          color: var(--text-primary);
          line-height: 1.6;
          min-height: 100vh;
          padding: 2rem 0;
          margin: 0;
      }

      .author-container {
          max-width: 1200px;
          margin: 0 auto;
          padding: 0 1.5rem;
      }

      .author-header {
          display: grid;
          grid-template-columns: 180px 1fr;
          gap: 2.5rem;
          background: var(--light-bg);
          backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
          border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
          border-radius: 24px;
          padding: 3rem;
          margin-bottom: 3rem;
          box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
          align-items: start;
      }

      .author-avatar-placeholder {
          width: 180px;
          height: 180px;
          background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f7fafc 0%, #edf2f7 100%);
          border: 2px dashed #e2e8f0;
          border-radius: 16px;
          display: flex;
          flex-direction: column;
          align-items: center;
          justify-content: center;
          color: var(--text-muted);
          font-size: 0.9rem;
          text-align: center;
          transition: all 0.3s ease;
      }

      .author-avatar-placeholder:hover {
          border-color: #cbd5e0;
          background: linear-gradient(135deg, #edf2f7 0%, #e2e8f0 100%);
      }

      .author-info h1 {
          font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.75rem);
          font-weight: 700;
          color: var(--text-primary);
          margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
          letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      }

      .author-bio {
          color: var(--text-secondary);
          font-size: 1.1rem;
          line-height: 1.6;
          margin: 1rem 0 0 0;
      }

      .books-grid-section {
          background: var(--light-bg);
          backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
          border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
          border-radius: 24px;
          padding: 3rem;
          box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
          margin-bottom: 2rem;
      }

      .section-header {
          display: flex;
          justify-content: space-between;
          align-items: center;
          margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
          flex-wrap: wrap;
          gap: 1rem;
      }

      .section-title {
          color: var(--text-primary);
          font-size: 1.375rem;
          font-weight: 600;
          margin: 0;
      }

      .count-badge {
          background: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
          color: var(--text-primary);
          padding: 0.25rem 1rem;
          border-radius: 20px;
          font-size: 0.85rem;
          font-weight: 500;
      }

      .books-grid {
          display: grid;
          grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(200px, 1fr));
          gap: 1.5rem;
          list-style: none;
          padding: 0;
          margin: 0;
      }

      .book-card {
          aspect-ratio: 2.8 / 4;
          background: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
          border-radius: 12px;
          overflow: hidden;
          text-decoration: none;
          color: inherit;
          transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
          position: relative;
          border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
      }

      .book-card::before {
          content: '';
          position: absolute;
          top: 0;
          left: -100%;
          width: 100%;
          height: 100%;
          background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,0.4), transparent);
          transition: left 0.6s;
      }

      .book-card:hover {
          transform: translateY(-8px) scale(1.02);
          box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
          border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      }

      .book-card:hover::before {
          left: 100%;
      }

      .book-image-placeholder {
          width: 100%;
          height: 70%;
          background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8fafc 0%, #f1f5f9 100%);
          border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
          display: flex;
          align-items: center;
          justify-content: center;
          position: relative;
      }

      .book-image-placeholder::after {
          content: 'ðŸ“–';
          font-size: 2.5rem;
          opacity: 0.3;
      }

      .book-title {
          padding: 1rem 0.875rem 0.75rem;
          font-size: 0.9rem;
          font-weight: 600;
          color: var(--text-primary);
          line-height: 1.3;
          display: -webkit-box;
          -webkit-line-clamp: 3;
          -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
          overflow: hidden;
      }

      .empty-state {
          min-height: 300px;
          display: flex;
          flex-direction: column;
          justify-content: center;
          align-items: center;
          color: var(--text-muted);
          font-size: 1.1rem;
          line-height: 1.6;
          padding: 2rem;
      }

      .back-btn, .action-btn {
          display: inline-flex;
          align-items: center;
          gap: 0.5rem;
          font-weight: 500;
          font-size: 0.9rem;
          color: var(--text-secondary);
          text-decoration: none;
          padding: 0.5rem 1.25rem;
          border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
          border-radius: 8px;
          transition: all 0.2s ease;
          background: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
          backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
          margin: 0.25rem;
      }

      .back-btn:hover, .action-btn:hover {
          background: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
          color: var(--text-primary);
          transform: translateY(-1px);
          box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      }

      .back-btn {
          border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
      }

      .actions-bar {
          display: flex;
          flex-wrap: wrap;
          gap: 0.75rem;
          justify-content: center;
          padding: 2rem 0;
          border-top: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
      }

      @media (max-width: 992px) {
          .author-container {
              padding: 0 1rem;
          }

          .author-header {
              grid-template-columns: 140px 1fr;
              gap: 2rem;
              padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
          }
      }

      @media (max-width: 768px) {
          .author-header {
              grid-template-columns: 1fr;
              text-align: center;
              gap: 2rem;
          }

          .author-avatar-placeholder {
              width: 140px;
              height: 140px;
              margin: 0 auto;
          }

          .books-grid {
              grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(160px, 1fr));
              gap: 1.25rem;
          }

          .actions-bar {
              flex-direction: column;
              align-items: center;
          }

          .action-btn, .back-btn {
              width: 100%;
              max-width: 280px;
              justify-content: center;
          }
      }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="author-container">
  <div class="author-header">
    <div class="author-avatar-placeholder">
      <i class="fas fa-user" style="font-size: 2.5rem; color: #cbd5e0; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"></i>
      <div>Foto do autor</div>
      <small>(Placeholder)</small>
    </div>

    <div class="author-info">
      <h1><%= @author.name %></h1>
      <div class="author-bio">
        EspaÃ§o reservado para biografia do autor. Aqui vocÃª pode adicionar informaÃ§Ãµes sobre sua
        trajetÃ³ria, principais obras, prÃªmios e outras informaÃ§Ãµes relevantes.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="books-grid-section">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2 class="section-title">Obras</h2>
      <% if @author.books.any? %>
        <span class="count-badge"><%= @author.books.count %> livro<%= @author.books.count > 1 ? 's' : '' %></span>
      <% end %>
    </div>

    <% if @author.books.any? %>
      <ul class="books-grid">
        <% @author.books.each do |book| %>
          <li>
            <%= link_to book_path(book), class: "book-card" do %>
              <div class="book-image-placeholder">
              </div>
              <div class="book-title"><%= book.name %></div>
            <% end %>
          </li>
        <% end %>
      </ul>
    <% else %>
      <div class="empty-state">
        <i class="fas fa-book" style="font-size: 3rem; color: #cbd5e0; margin-bottom: 1rem;"></i>
        <div>Nenhum livro cadastrado ainda.</div>
      </div>
    <% end %>
  </div>

  <div class="actions-bar">
    <%= link_to "<i class='fas fa-arrow-left'></i> Voltar".html_safe, root_path, class: 'back-btn' %>
    <%= link_to "<i class='fas fa-plus'></i> Novo Livro".html_safe, new_book_path, class: "action-btn" %>
    <%= link_to "<i class='fas fa-users'></i> Todos os Autores".html_safe, authors_path, class: "action-btn" %>
    <%= link_to "<i class='fas fa-book'></i> Todos os Livros".html_safe, books_path, class: "action-btn" %>
  </div>
</div>

<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
